title: Looking for Low S - High Bronze Duo Partner
body:
Transferred to OCE recently from NA where I was Gold I. Looking for a duo partner to climb with between 9pm-1am.
I main top {{champion:39}}/{{champion:114}}/{{champion:105}}   so a good jungler would be wonderful for that gank goodness but all mains are welcome. 

Mic+Skype are essential as is a good sense of humour and patience. No ragequitters please. 
IGN: Malifus
